app自己睇唔到自己用緊咩icon，你問我用緊咩icon，講真我自己都唔記得，話唔定轉漏左<br />\n但重點係，用唔用你icon其實無咩特別意思，用左唔代表真係好鐘意你，唔用都唔代表唔鐘意，大把人日日係ig放閃扮恩愛，但現實中拍得好唔開心，只係想搏人以為佢好幸福</blockquote><br />\n佢成日轉icon㗎，不過轉黎轉去都係同我嘅合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都可能係，因為佢啲fd都拍哂拖，所以其實佢都恨左拍拖好耐，可能只係唔想比佢啲fd笑先繼續用我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e45988070c0c1387b8a442569ec3fa2c490b881","tid":300741,"uid":32331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢成日罵交，啲人話咁樣有助增進感情，係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同人嘈<br />\n同人鬧交<br />\n唔是罵交囉唔該"},{"pid":"7ea13303c6bb84e94db83a8d5a5692828d4e2ace","tid":300741,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同佢成日罵交，啲人話咁樣有助增進感情，係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同人嘈<br />\n同人鬧交<br />\n唔是罵交囉唔該</blockquote><br />\nsor<br />\n小弟中文差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6674adb3fd12c8e409af5a8eed8bcd7b42764d3c","tid":300741,"uid":67895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"拍左幾耐"},{"pid":"5162b52a4bbb2db28fa81b6fcc981439fa95744c","tid":300741,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n三個禮拜多啲"},{"pid":"be3e95f4c4f77faaa72c06d2924d1ff1a218cf43","tid":300741,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拍左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n三個禮拜多啲</blockquote><br />\n三個禮拜都咁多野嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a0d96a4a6f277554506e15e0ff830d136e3920","tid":300741,"uid":67589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:24:12.000Z","msg":"嘈完會互相反省會改 咪增進到感情<br />\n就算比你幾個月先嘈一次 你唔識體諒對方都冇用架啦<br />\n不過可能都有人從來唔鬧交，一嚟就好大獲爆哂出嚟<br />\n自己衡量啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2c0f3bb38d9cc9b7dbb639bdc4705433fe02ce","tid":300741,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:30:34.000Z","msg":"鬧來鬧去都係同一個問題？"},{"pid":"ac9dbde49e3824c5c4c91b98179ceffbeec5bd25","tid":300741,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:30:48.000Z","msg":"小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece1fe7a38e46e857a44d5ca5465e3f4bd64d412","tid":300741,"uid":8726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:38:32.000Z","msg":"拿拿聲屌多幾劑先啦"},{"pid":"53657bc79e6c5ccada8657ba80a4f840236ae971","tid":300741,"uid":123787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:39:28.000Z","msg":"代表唔夾囉。仲駛問?<br />\n鬧交其實好傷感情。情侶鬧得交即係有一方唔肯妥協。愛係需要互相遷就同包容，如果成日嘈，即係有一方唔係咁鐘意對方。"},{"pid":"7052dadead33f8273285f0edf537bace10e6253c","tid":300741,"uid":8302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係咁"}]}